title: Subjects
page_description:
Peer-reviewed. Openly licensed. 100% free.

And backed by additional learning resources. Review our OpenStax textbooks and decide if they are right for your course. Simple to adopt, free to use. We make it easy to improve student access to higher education.
dev_standard_1_description: Our open source textbooks are written by professional content developers who are experts in their fields.
dev_standard_2_description: All textbooks meet standard scope and sequence requirements, making them seamlessly adaptable into existing courses.
dev_standard_3_description: OpenStax textbooks undergo a rigorous peer review process. You can view the list of contributors when you click on each book.
dev_standard_4_description: With philanthropic support, our books have been used in classrooms, saving students $ since 2012. Learn more about our impact and how you can help.
